Achievements.Name: Smokin'
Achievements.Description: Defeat Kane in an Inferno Match.

Achievements.Name: Create A Finisher
Achievements.Description: Defeat an opponent using a Created Finisher in a match.

Achievements.Name: A brawl to end them all
Achievements.Description: Win in both a Locker Room Brawl and Backstage Brawl.

Achievements.Name: Cena Story
Achievements.Description: Complete Cena's story in Road to WrestleMania mode.

Achievements.Name: Triple H Story
Achievements.Description: Complete Triple H's DX and Evolution route in  Road to WrestleMania mode.

Achievements.Name: Undertaker Story
Achievements.Description: Complete Undertaker's story in Road to WrestleMania mode.

Achievements.Name: Chris Jericho Story
Achievements.Description: Complete Chris Jericho's story in  Road to WrestleMania mode.

Achievements.Name: Mysterio & Batista Story
Achievements.Description: Complete Mysterio & Batista's story in  Road to WrestleMania mode using both Superstars.

Achievements.Name: Bonus Collector
Achievements.Description: Obtain all bonuses in Road to WrestleMania mode.

Achievements.Name: Gold Rush
Achievements.Description: In Career mode, win every WWE Championship at least once.

Achievements.Name: A year in the life
Achievements.Description: Complete 1 year of Career Mode playing each match.

Achievements.Name: Unstoppable
Achievements.Description: Use a created Superstar and obtain 6 abilities in Career Mode.

Achievements.Name: 5 Hall of Famers
Achievements.Description: In Career mode, induct 5 Superstars to the Hall of Fame.

Achievements.Name: Lights,Camera,Action!
Achievements.Description: Create at least 1 original WWE highlight reel.

Achievements.Name: Hot Tag
Achievements.Description: Perform a hot tag in a tag team match and win.

Achievements.Name: The end of the road
Achievements.Description: Complete Road to WrestleMania mode using each selectable Superstar.

Achievements.Name: 5 Stars
Achievements.Description: In Career mode, Obtain a 5-Star match rating.
